These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-1::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: aquamarine, mauve, lilac, coral
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: horror, mystery, animation, documentary
1. the person who likes mauve is somewhere to the right of the person who likes aquamarine##5
2. the person watching documentary movies is on the left or right of the person watching horror movies##3
3. the person watching horror movies is in an odd position##4
4. the person who likes coral is somewhere to the left of the person watching documentary movies##5
5. the person watching horror movies is the person who likes mauve##1
6. the person who likes lilac is the person watching mystery movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |       2       |     3     |   4    |
| Color      | coral  | aquamarine | mauve  | lilac |
| Movie-Genre   | animation | documentary      | horror | mystery |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: tea, coffee, water, lemonade
There are 4 different favourite colors: coral, grey, lavender, aquamarine
1. the person drinking coffee is between the person who likes coral and the person who likes aquamarine##2
2. the person drinking lemonade is somewhere to the left of the person who likes aquamarine##5
3. the person who likes coral is on the right of the person who likes lavender##1
4. the person who likes coral is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
5. the person who likes grey is on the left of the person drinking tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |     3      |     4      |
| Beverage   | lemonade | water | coffee   | tea |
| Color           | lavender      | coral    | grey | aquamarine      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-3::.
4 different games are played: whist, mah-jongg, canasta, go
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: dannemann, dunhill, fonseca, swisher
1. the person playing mah-jongg is the dunhill-smoker##1
2. the swisher-smoker is on the right of the person playing mah-jongg##1
3. the fonseca-smoker is somewhere to the left of the dannemann-smoker##5
4. the dannemann-smoker is on the left or right of the person playing canasta##3
5. the person playing go is somewhere to the right of the swisher-smoker##5
6. the person playing mah-jongg is somewhere to the left of the fonseca-smoker##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |    2    |     3     |   4    |
| Game        | mah-jongg | whist | canasta     | go |
| Cigar   | dunhill  | swisher   | fonseca | dannemann    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-4::.
House: art-deco, futuristic, wooden, tower
There are 4 different favourite beverages: mirinda, juice, cola, fanta
1. the art-deco house is on the left of the futuristic house##1
2. the tower house is somewhere to the right of the person drinking cola##5
3. the art-deco house is between the person drinking fanta and the person drinking juice##2
4. the person drinking cola is on the left or right of the person drinking fanta##3
5. the person drinking fanta is the wooden house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3    |      4      |
| House         | wooden | art-deco | futuristic | tower |
| Beverage   | fanta   | cola     | juice    | mirinda       |

