.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-5::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: iris, daisy, dahlia, amaryllis
City: london, san-francisco, liverpool, prague
1. the person who growsamaryllis is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to london##5
2. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left or right of the person who growsdahlia##3
3. the person who growsdahlia is somewhere to the left of the person who growsiris##5
4. the person traveling to liverpool is on the right of the person traveling to london##1
5. the person traveling to london is on the left or right of the person who growsdaisy##3
6. the person who growsamaryllis is on the right of the person traveling to san-francisco##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |    3     |    4    |
| Flower          | dahlia | amaryllis   | iris   | daisy    |
| City   | san-francisco  | prague | london | liverpool |

