.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-6::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: puzzles, board-games, dancing, woodworking
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: tiparillo, dannemann, prince, blend
1. the person who's hobby is woodworking is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's hobby is puzzles is somewhere to the left of the blend-smoker##5
3. the blend-smoker is between the person who's hobby is woodworking and the prince-smoker##2
4. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the right of the tiparillo-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |       3        |     4     |
| Hobby           | puzzles | board-games | woodworking | dancing |
| Cigar   | prince        | blend     | tiparillo       | dannemann   |

