.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-7::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: red, white, lilac, pink
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: thriller, musical, drama, disaster
1. the person watching musical movies is the person who likes pink##1
2. the person who likes red is between the person who likes white and the person watching drama movies##2
3. the person watching thriller movies is in an even position##4
4. the person watching disaster movies is somewhere to the left of the person who likes red##5
5. the person who likes red is in an even position##4
6. the person who likes lilac is on the left or right of the person watching musical movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |   3   |    4    |
| Color   | white | red  | lilac  | pink   |
| Movie-Genre           | disaster  | thriller | drama | musical |

