.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-8::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: november, april, june, september
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: tulip, lily, sunflower, dahlia
1. the person who growslily is on the right of the person who growsdahlia##1
2. the person who's birthday is in september is somewhere to the left of the person who growssunflower##5
3. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in june##3
4. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left of the person who's birthday is in september##1
5. the person who growssunflower is somewhere to the left of the person who growstulip##5

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |     2      |    3     |    4     |
| Birthday   | april     | september | june     | november   |
| Flower    | dahlia | lily  | sunflower | tulip |

