.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-9::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: hip-hop, blues, soul, house
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: may, october, march, july
1. the person who's birthday is in march is on the right of the fan of hip-hop##1
2. the fan of soul is on the left of the fan of house##1
3. the fan of hip-hop is on the left of the fan of soul##1
4. the fan of blues is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in july##5
5. the person who's birthday is in october is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in may##5
6. the person who's birthday is in may is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in march##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2     |   3    |  4   |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop | soul | house   | blues |
| Birthday       | may       | march   | july | october |

