.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-10::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: boat, quad-bike, bus, helicopter
There are 4 different favourite colors: light-blue, emerald, lilac, black
1. the person driving the bus is on the left or right of the person who likes emerald##3
2. the person who likes light-blue is somewhere to the left of the person driving the helicopter##5
3. the person who likes black is somewhere to the right of the person driving the quad-bike##5
4. the person who likes light-blue is somewhere to the right of the person who likes black##5
5. the person who likes emerald is somewhere to the left of the person driving the boat##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |   3    |     4      |
| Transport   | quad-bike | bus       | boat   | helicopter        |
| Color      | emerald  | black | light-blue | lilac |

