.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-11::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: spy, musical, martial-arts, comedy
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: may, april, july, december
1. the person watching spy movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching musical movies##5
2. the person who's birthday is in july is the person watching martial-arts movies##1
3. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left of the person watching musical movies##1
4. the person watching comedy movies is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in july##5
5. the person who's birthday is in april is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in may##5
6. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in april##3
7. the person watching martial-arts movies is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in may##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |    3    |     4      |
| Movie-Genre   | spy | musical   | martial-arts | comedy     |
| Birthday   | april     | may | july  | december |

