.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-12::.
There 4 different types of food: plum, kale, cauliflower, banana
City: marseilles, new-york, edinburgh, nizza
1. the person traveling to nizza is on the left of the person traveling to marseilles##1
2. the person traveling to nizza is in an even position##4
3. the person eating banana is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to new-york##5
4. the person eating plum is the person traveling to edinburgh##1
5. the person eating banana is somewhere to the right of the person eating cauliflower##5
6. the person traveling to new-york is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |     3      |  4   |
| Food   | plum | cauliflower        | banana        | kale |
| City         | edinburgh  | nizza | marseilles | new-york |

