3. the cain-smoker is in an odd position##4
4. the person who likes brown is somewhere to the left of the montecristo-smoker##5
5. the montecristo-smoker is on the right of the person who likes brown##1
6. the person who likes fuchsia is the montecristo-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
