1. the person driving the train is somewhere to the right of the person eating peach##5
2. the person driving the boat is somewhere to the right of the person eating cucumber##5
3. the person eating eggplant is on the left of the person eating radish##1
4. the person eating radish is the person driving the boat##1
5. the person driving the jet-ski is somewhere to the right of the person driving the train##5
6. the person eating eggplant is on the left or right of the person eating cucumber##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |      3      |    4     |
| Transport   | quad-bike  | train | jet-ski | boat |
| Food   | peach | cucumber | eggplant   | radish  |

