2. the person eating pumpkin is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person eating cabbage is on the right of the oliveros-smoker##1
4. the game-smoker is in an even position##4
5. the person eating blueberry is somewhere to the left of the person eating pumpkin##5
6. the person eating pepper is between the person eating blueberry and the chaman-smoker##2
7. the person eating cabbage is somewhere to the right of the person eating blueberry##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |     3      |     4     |
| Food      | blueberry   | pepper  | cabbage      | pumpkin       |
| Cigar   | old-henry | oliveros | chaman | game |

