.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-17::.
4 different games are played: poker, billiard, go, chess
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: soul, electronic, metal, techno
1. the person playing chess is somewhere to the left of the fan of techno##5
2. the person playing go is the fan of techno##1
3. the fan of soul is on the right of the fan of electronic##1
4. the person playing chess is somewhere to the right of the person playing poker##5
5. the fan of metal is on the right of the person playing billiard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |    3    |  4   |
| Game   | poker     | billiard | chess | go |
| Music-Genre     | electronic | soul    | metal    | techno |

