.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-18::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: quad-bike, helicopter, car, bike
4 different pets are kept: ferret, turtle, bird, hedgehog
1. the owner of the bird is on the far left or far right##3
2. the owner of the ferret is somewhere to the right of the owner of the hedgehog##5
3. the owner of the bird is somewhere to the left of the person driving the quad-bike##5
4. the owner of the ferret is somewhere to the left of the person driving the helicopter##5
5. the owner of the ferret is on the left of the owner of the turtle##1
6. the person driving the quad-bike is between the person driving the bike and the owner of the turtle##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |    3     |       4       |
| Transport      | car     | bike | quad-bike     | helicopter |
| Pet   | bird | hedgehog  | ferret | turtle        |

