.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-19::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: traveling, chess, reading, skydiving
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, surfing, tennis, skateboarding
1. the person who's hobby is traveling is between the person who's sport is surfing and the person who's hobby is chess##2
2. the person who's sport is baseball is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##5
3. the person who's hobby is reading is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is skateboarding##5
4. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left or right of the person who's sport is baseball##3
5. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2    |     3      |     4      |
| Hobby         | reading   | skydiving   | traveling       | chess   |
| Sport   | tennis | surfing | baseball | skateboarding |

