.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-20::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: orchid, aconite, marigold, balloon-flower
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, mirinda, lemonade, water
1. the person who growsaconite is somewhere to the left of the person drinking mirinda##5
2. the person who growsorchid is on the right of the person drinking water##1
3. the person drinking lemonade is in an odd position##4
4. the person drinking hot-chocolate is somewhere to the right of the person drinking mirinda##5
5. the person who growsaconite is somewhere to the left of the person drinking water##5
6. the person who growsorchid is between the person who growsballoon-flower and the person drinking hot-chocolate##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2      |     3     |     4      |
| Flower        | aconite     | balloon-flower | orchid | marigold |
| Beverage   | lemonade | water | mirinda      | hot-chocolate        |

 